aa(lp322
VSo you may be wondering:
p323
aVthese are beautiful laboratory experiments,
p324
aVdo they really apply to real life?
p325
aVYeah, I've been worrying about that too.
p326
aVSo I've gone out of the lab
p327
aVto see if this really holds in our daily lives.
