aa(lp340
VAnd guess what?
p341
aVWeddings cause a release of oxytocin,
p342
aVbut they do so in a very particular way.
p343
aVWho is the center of the wedding solar system?
p344
aVThe bride.
p345
aVShe had the biggest increase in oxytocin.
p346
aVWho loves the wedding almost as much as the bride?
p347
aVHer mother, that's right.
